{"tid":1284442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對付藍絲家長","createTime":"2019-07-04T07:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T07:34:46.000Z","uid":33206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aeab8a9b9f525b0b7f77a97eeb2edc635fb37106","tid":1284442,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:20:48.000Z","msg":"「突發」大件事了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284074</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我用百度search，跟本冇6月28號新聞，因為河蟹晒，只有百度貼吧啲人好隱晦咁講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CfTEojc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCfTEojc.png&h=944a4c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtSmBEc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtSmBEc.png&h=c0483769&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMFfF5T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMFfF5T.png&h=2aa8b079&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGHqiSy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGHqiSy.png&h=434ced89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地可以開黎消化下，然後向你地藍絲家人講以下幾個訊息：<br />\n<br />\n1. 屌呢班人，出黎遊行做咩姐？肯定收咗人錢，收咗外國人錢，你知道而家好多人想睇住武漢政府同中央死，呢班人搞屎棍！<br />\n<br />\n2. 你對比下google search結果同百度search結果，證明內地消息極不流通，你想唔想第時香港都變成咁？<br />\n<br />\n3. 武漢人口一千萬人，出黎示威者只有1萬左右，證明99%以上的人都是支持建廠，所以遊行嘅人應該收皮返屋企！"},{"pid":"e401876102d93cc938865a0babb23a8a3a561584","tid":1284442,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:22:29.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"ec81bbe6b0d34a6c81362daaee5e85ca52b22574","tid":1284442,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72e1f068b13a0e87dd36fb0b6e5d0b7fe447a6ed","tid":1284442,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:34:46.000Z","msg":"推"}]}